Storm font support for ConTeXt
------------------------------

support: (c) Vit Zyka, vit.zyka@seznam.cz
distributed under General Public Licence
(http://typokitek.com/typokv-download-TeX-en.html)

based on: plain TeX Storm font support by Petr Olsak
(http://www.cstug.cz/stormtype/)

fonts: (c) Storm Font Foundry (http://www.stormtype.com)

--- Distribution:

stormcontext.zip      support itself
stormcontext-lido.zip support only for Lido font
stormcontext-cat.zip  catalog and its sources
storm-lido.zip        Type1 Lido: read the licence before installing!

--- Catalogue:

cont-storm-catalog.pdf

--- Quick Usage:

\useencoding[st1]
\useencoding[st3]
\enableregime[ec]

\usetypescriptfile[t-type-slido]
\usetypescript[Lido][st1]
\setupbodyfont[Lido,10pt,rm]

--- Font family list:
Aichel, Biblon, DynamoRE, Libcziowes, Lido, Preissig-Text,
Preissig-Antikva, Preissig1918, Serapion, Solpera, Tyfa-Text.
